# Read CWS CLAUDE.md on Connection

When first connecting to a Cloud Workspace (CWS) via `oflowctl cws ssh`, read `~/CLAUDE.md` on the remote host to get workspace-specific context (code paths, scripts, conventions). Do this before running other commands.
